The Savant Studios x Todd Snyder Artifacts Collection. Available 03.02.23 exclusively at Todd Snyder.

Artifacts draws inspiration from Savant founder, Mike Graham’s childhood, recent travels, jazz and more. The collection highlights Savant’s signature process of “Slow Magic”—a specific attention to hand detail and craft when designing—on a handful of core Todd Snyder styles. The result creates wearable works of art that blend past and future, like treasures pulled from a time capsule. Due to their intricate handcrafted nature, each item is unique and considered one-of-a-kind.
